<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="16th_century">16th century</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=God_the_Father_in_Western_art&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: 16th century"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
